
roce = total return on total capital (equity + debt)
roe  = total return on equity only
if debt=0 check roe
else check roce

(dividend is given from Total Reserves)
if dividend is high roe will automaticall be high.




total equity = Share Capital  + Total Reserves
roe = Net Profit(profit after tax)/(total equity)
roce  operating profit / (equity + Borrowings)
